oai_dc:dc.dc:description: |xam names of stars and constellations. The names of a number of Stars have been ascertained with the kind help of Mr. Maclear. Besides a separate alphabetical index to the Stars, the names of some are given in a supplementary list (B XXV. 2345-2347 and 2354).
